_sText:
It is with great honor that I present this map made by the same person who made bhop_tex (with their permission of course)

This is a 5 stage map made with different themes in mind.
  • Stage 1:  Basic bhop
  • Stage 2:  Technical bhop
  • Stage 3:  Precision
  • Stage 4:  Speed
  • Stage 5: All in one
Development for this map began in June, 2011, and was intended for 100aa scroll but can be enjoyed on all styles. A huge thanks to Dotty and Tex for making this all possible. Hope you enjoy!
